  "page": "High Septon (Aegon III)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon\" title=\"High Septon\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/50px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/75px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/100px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">High Septon</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon\" title=\"High Septon\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/50px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/75px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/100px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon\" title=\"High Septon\">High Septon</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Father_of_the_Faithful\" title=\"Father of the Faithful\">Father of the Faithful</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/His_High_Holiness\" title=\"His High Holiness\">His High Holiness</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Shepherd_of_the_Faithful\" title=\"Shepherd of the Faithful\">Shepherd of the Faithful</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Voice_of_the_Seven_on_Earth\" title=\"Voice of the Seven on Earth\">Voice of the Seven on Earth</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_143_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">143</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_169_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">169&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>High Septon</b> was <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon\" title=\"High Septon\">High Septon</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=High_Septon_(Aegon_III)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The High Septon reversed the ruling of <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Regency_of_Aegon_III)\" title=\"High Septon (Regency of Aegon III)\">his predecessor</a>, who forbade Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Hightower\" title=\"Lyonel Hightower\">Lyonel Hightower</a> to marry his <a href=\"/index.php/Ormund_Hightower\" title=\"Ormund Hightower\">father</a>'s widow, <a href=\"/index.php/Samantha_Tarly\" title=\"Samantha Tarly\">Samantha Tarly</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>It is unknown if the six children of Lyonel and Samantha born before their marriage were <a href=\"/index.php/Bastardy#Legitimization\" title=\"Bastardy\">legitimized</a> afterward.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=High_Septon_(Aegon_III)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Aftermath - The Hour of the Wolf.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<td style=\"width:30%;\" rowspan=\"1\">Preceded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Regency_of_Aegon_III)\" title=\"High Septon (Regency of Aegon III)\">During the regency of Aegon III</a></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon\" title=\"High Septon\">High Septon</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Father_of_the_Faithful\" title=\"Father of the Faithful\">Father of the Faithful</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/His_High_Holiness\" title=\"His High Holiness\">His High Holiness</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Shepherd_of_the_Faithful\" title=\"Shepherd of the Faithful\">Shepherd of the Faithful</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Voice_of_the_Seven_on_Earth\" title=\"Voice of the Seven on Earth\">Voice of the Seven on Earth</a> </b><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_143_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">143&#160;AC</a>–?\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Next known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Baelor_I)\" title=\"High Septon (Baelor I)\">During the reign of Baelor I</a> </b>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:High_Septons\" title=\"Template:High Septons\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.